C

com.csfrancis555.math613project1 - package com.csfrancis555.math613project1
Project for a MATH 613, Applied Linear Algebra, course taken at Indiana State University in the fall semester of 2023. This project will: Apply Gaussian Elimination and Back Substitution to solve systems of equations Compute determinants, LU Decomposition, and Inverses Apply the Jacobi Method to process large datasets
